        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A hinge has a single degree of freedom (rotation). You can also use a hinge joint to pin a body so that it can only move by rotating around a specific axis in the coordinate space of the node containing it."
